> **FIRST** grepai for code search. Grep/Glob only for exact text or external paths.

## Decision

| Task | Tool | Scope |
|------|------|-------|
| Intent/meaning | `grepai_search` | indexed project |
| Exact text/regex | `Grep` | project + external via `path` |
| File path patterns | `Glob` | project + external via `path` |
| Web/external docs | `WebSearch` | internet |

**Rule:** exact match needed? → Grep/Glob · otherwise → **grepai FIRST**

## MCP Tools (`--compact` saves ~80% tokens)

| Tool | Use |
|------|-----|
| `grepai_search` | `query`, `limit?`, `compact?` — semantic search |
| `grepai_trace_callers` | `symbol`, `compact?` — who calls it |
| `grepai_trace_callees` | `symbol`, `compact?` — what it calls |
| `grepai_trace_graph` | `symbol`, `depth?`, `compact?` — call graph |
| `grepai_index_status` | `verbose?` — check indexed files/languages |

## Queries

English · Intent over syntax · Specific over vague
`"handles user login"` ✓ · `"func Login"` ✗

## Scope Limits

grepai searches **indexed project files only**:
- Files not matching `ignore:` patterns in config